column6: Do you consent to participate in this survey?
column7: What type of job have you primarily held in last 3 semesters?
column8: How satisfied are you with the overall work environment at your part-time job?

column13: How would you rate the physical conditions of your workplace (e.g., cleanliness, comfort, equipment)?(1 = Very unlikely, 5 = Very likely)
column14: Rank the following factors based on how they contribute to a positive work environment for you.
column15: Do you feel that there are opportunities for personal growth or learning in your part-time job?
column16:
